										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Here we go&#8230;  The release of the 2nd book in the Clockwork Twist series is swiftly approaching.  Mark you calendars because it will hit on-line stores on Tuesday, January 14th!  In anticipation of this most exciting event, I&#8217;m going to post the first few chapters, one per week, right here on this blog.</p>
<h3 style="text-align:center;"><a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft" alt="" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/clock-face-copper-sm.jpg" width="236" height="236" /></a><br />
<a title="Trick: Chapter 1" href="http://clockworktwist.com/trick-chpt-1/">Click here to start reading right now!</a><br />
~oOo~</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="color:#000000;">What new wonders and strange happenings will Twist encounter this time?  Will he be surrounded by pirates once again?  Will he even get back home to London?  <a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/">Click here</a> for a quick synopsis of coming events. (no spoilers, I promise.)</span></p>
<p>Keep and eye on the <a href="http://www.facebook.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">Facebook</a>, <a href="http://twitter.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, <a href="http://cwtwist.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">Tumblr</a>, or blog to find out the moment the next chapter is up!  Oh, how fantastically exciting!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
